data.description:
Discover an exceptional opportunity in a prime location with unbeatable convenience to Cotswold, Southpark, Matthews, and Uptown. This charming and meticulously maintained home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac and has been freshly painted just for you. As you step into the spacious yet cozy living room, you'll be greeted by a wall of windows that overlook the beautiful park-like grounds. The gorgeous kitchen with a wall oven and stylish backsplash opens to the large dining room with a beamed ceiling, adding to the charm of this wonderful home and making it perfect for entertaining guests. With a walkout basement rec room, a two-car garage, and a very private backyard, this home is sure to impress! Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make it yours – schedule your tour today and experience the beauty and comfort of this exceptional home!

MOTIVATED SELLER.
